title: Nike Football: Andrés Iniesta: My Ground
description:
"I started off playing small-sided. Everything grew from there." -- Andrés Iniesta reflects on his roots.

In this film, Iniesta wears the Elastico Finale II, available March 28. Europe pre-order: http://go.nike.com/ElasticoEU
